description: This beautifully renovated South Boston condominium offers modern urban living at its finest. The open-concept design features a sleek kitchen with custom modern cabinetry, Thermador stainless steel appliances (incl. built-in coffee system), a gas stove, and LED-lit open shelving. Stained wood floors flow throughout, while the primary suite includes a private, tiled bathroom with a luxurious multi-head shower. The custom-tiled main bathroom is equally impressive. Enjoy wired ceiling speakers, a private balcony with city and water views, and a private roof deck perfect for outdoor relaxation. The home is equipped with efficient forced-air gas heating, central AC, and on-demand tankless hot water. Two garage parking spaces provide added convenience. Close to shops, restaurants, Castle Island, parks, and the beach, this is the ultimate South Boston location for style, comfort, and convenience.
